  "title": "Romantic Rich Middle Eastern Christmas Pudding Labneh",
  "description": "A salty, tender, and romantic Middle Eastern dish featuring Christmas pudding, fry-grind-rice-khao-khua, and labneh, perfect for a diabetic-friendly dessert option",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
